# --- Dependencies & Build ---
# Catches node_modules and build folders in root, /client, and /server
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml

# --- Environment & Secrets ---
# Crucial: Keeps your MongoDB URI and API keys off GitHub
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/*.local

# --- Logs ---
# Standard error and debug logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Editor & IDE ---
# Keeps your team's specific VS Code or WebStorm settings private
.vscode/
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# --- Operating System ---
# System-specific junk (Mac/Windows)
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db